  "texts": [
    "It works out for a variety of translation tasks, including translations from text to images, from images to images, and from images to images semantically.",
    "Translations of images into other images: GANs have the potential to be utilized in image-to-image translations that will be utilized for varied translation operations, including: a.",
    "The conversion of satellite/aerial imagery to Google Earth or Google maps. b.",
    "Changing specifics day to darkness and back again in the editing process.",
    "c. The process of coloring photographs that were originally taken in black and white."
